CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Save Foods Inc is a development stage company which is involved in the business of developing, testing, and marketing solutions and products for extending storability and shelf life of vegetables and fruits through its subsidiary. The company develops products that treat citrus fruits, sweet potatoes, stored table potatoes and also provide storage control of fruits and vegetables. It has also started commercialization of its products.
